IBAN,com,operates,as,a,web,based,solution,that,supports,the,validation,and,calculation,of,International,Bank,Account,Numbers,IBANs,The,platform,provides,the,IBAN,Calculation,engine,that,facilitates,the,conversion,of,domestic,bank,code,and,account,number,combinations,into,authenticated,IBANs,The,IBAN,Calculation,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,the,IBAN,conversion,engine,in,their,applications,and,operating,systems,It,also,makes,it,easier,for,users,to,identify,banks,and,other,financial,institutions,This,API,returns,responses,in,JSON,and,XML,formats